@startuml seq_29_manage_platform
title Sequence Diagram: UC-29 Manage Platform (Admin Login/Logout)

actor Admin
participant "Admin Web" as Frontend
participant "Admin Auth Controller" as Controller
participant "Admin Auth Service" as Service
participant "Admin Repo" as Repo
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis

Admin -> Frontend: Enter Admin Credentials
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/admin/auth/login
Controller -> Service: Admin Login
Service -> Repo: Fetch Admin by username
Repo --> Service: Admin found (hashed_password)
Service -> Service: Verify password & Admin Role
Service -> Service: Generate Admin Access & Refresh Tokens
Service -> Redis: Store Admin Auth State (Refresh Token)
Service --> Controller: Tokens
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: Redirect to Admin Dashboard

... Admin manages platform ...

Admin -> Frontend: Click Logout
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/admin/auth/logout
Controller -> Service: Admin Logout
Service -> Redis: Delete Admin Auth State (Revoke Session)
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: Redirect to Admin Login Page
@enduml